#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Aniccavagga "
msgstr "2. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Yadaniccasutta → yad anicca 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Yadaniccasutta "
msgstr "15. That Which is Impermanent "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.22, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.3"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.5"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.6"
msgid "Vedanā aniccā. "
msgstr "Feeling is impermanent … "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.7"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.8"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.9"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.10"
msgid "Saññā aniccā … pe … "
msgstr "Perception is impermanent … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.11"
msgid "saṅkhārā aniccā … "
msgstr "Choices are impermanent … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.12"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.13"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.14"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.15"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.16"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.15:1.17"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.15:1.18"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

